"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1929569-Rafael-Nadal-Novak-Djokovic-Olympics-2024-athlete-village\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalhas explained why he opted to stay in the Olympic village despite being arguably one of the biggest names at this year's Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard believes that competitors can not get the full experience if they do not fully immerse themselves, even if that means being uncomfortable.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551257347, \"rank\": 0.2500000000000275, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes afterNovak Djokovicsnubbed the athlete complexto stay in his own accommodationduring his quest for a gold medal.\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal has understandably been one of the most popular faces in the athlete village.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the last week, other sportspeople have thrown themselves at the chance to take a selfie with the 22-time Grand Slam champion around the grounds.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His compatriot and doubles partner for the Olympics,Carlos Alcaraz, is also living in the village.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it's a long 